{"tid":798463,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"PayMe 出左PayCode","createTime":"2018-08-29T10:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T01:29:52.000Z","uid":36138,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"80fa4637a2718bd29b4576af6f7b4943bfd1a6ab","tid":798463,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"PayCode 即是您在 PayMe 的 QR 碼。您只需展示您的PayCode，或使用應用程式的內置掃描器、其他 QR 掃描器或手機內的相機掃描 PayCode ，便可進行收款或付款。<br />\n<br />\n將來，當您需分付賬單或向朋友過數時，只需掃描、付款，便可完成支付程序！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/181034_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F181034_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png&h=30be5c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n您可在主頁選擇「付款」或「請求付款」，並點按「PayCode」圖標顯示PayCode，您可掃描或選擇已存取的PayCode，並輸入金額和授權付款便可。<br />\n<br />\nPayCode 亦讓您更輕易地新增朋友 &mdash; 您無需再輸入電話號碼或經 WhatsApp 或手機短訊，傳送款項連結 (雖然您仍可這樣做！）。<br />\n<br />\n您只需有收款人的PayCode，PayMe便可以自動把收款人新增為您的PayMe朋友。"},{"pid":"3e34cc72df7bcfdb118b3525ee5a0a0fe1e17af7","tid":798463,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 payme cs真係廢到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出多多功能都無撚用"},{"pid":"8eb9d35e62cf9b14105939b1073a80471e5e945c","tid":798463,"uid":3571,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df80fdf24ebd49578c73410db830de2600134922","tid":798463,"uid":4964,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"快手出向商戶比錢啦,唔好再比支咩寶搶佔市場啦"},{"pid":"34d8a5736181caaed9d1879ad5d0403193d09614","tid":798463,"uid":1159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"re